
The TeraGrid CSA SAGA-C++ installation
--------------------------------------

  In order to use this installation of SAGA (version 'trunk'), you
  need to set the following environment variables:

    export SAGA_LOCATION=/project/tg_csa/saga/saga/trunk/gcc-3.4.6/
    export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/project/tg_csa/saga/saga/trunk/gcc-3.4.6//lib:/project/tg_csa/saga/external/boost/1.44.0/gcc-3.4.6//lib:/project/tg_csa/saga/external/postgresql/9.0.2/gcc-3.4.6//lib:/project/tg_csa/saga/external/sqlite3/3.6.13/gcc-3.4.6//lib

  For more information about SAGA-C++, see http://saga.cct.lsu.edu/ .
